{"tid":1065861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打比女add 之後佢同你講係咪玩過party room","createTime":"2019-03-17T14:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T18:00:10.000Z","uid":216008,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"15fb2e487a7ca95a7b6b1a26f82835ba476e5a4c","tid":1065861,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"以為係以前啲中學同學/師姐 有common friend 咁咪accept<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆你個街 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢之後問我係咪有參加過觀塘party room</span></strong><br />\n咁我呢排真係去過兩次 但都係同朋友去 已經覺得奇怪 問清楚啲睇下佢咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢同我講<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「一齊玩dixit果個？」</span></strong><br />\n屌你老母會唔會玩dixit都要約出嚟一齊玩呀 無呀屌你老母<br />\n最後我鳩噏 基本問候返how much 1q 之後同佢講我無錢買顏料 借錢比我 我會用一世去畫你(隻臭雞）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢啱啱竟然同我講 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我幫你同翻城大既professor 講？<br />\n城大cm我都識好多人</span></strong><br />\n你點解呃錢都要呃到咁撚無品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講囉 我叫你講呀死臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你啲相遮曬樣都知咩事啦騙子仲喺道兇鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf58fef557fc87eb7fd0554237dc0c22bd9821e","tid":1065861,"uid":71237,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"比10分鐘你組織下, 之後再出過post啦"},{"pid":"20e0a326c03f0cb74ca40dcca8c6132e11132773","tid":1065861,"uid":216008,"like":0,"disl